  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to identify incidence of Chinese herb nephropathy in a medical
      center
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a retrospective study, by computer screening, chart review and phone survey to find
      herbal nephropathy and determine the cause-relationship.

      Using ICD-9-CM code as a tool to screen the newly diagnosed ESRD in NTUH computer data base,
      and divided patients into those with underlying disease(s) that cause the renal failure and
      those without.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
